---
title: Filipino-Inspired Pork Burgers with Adobo-Style Onions and Chili-Garlic Potatoes
description: We're packed the bold flavours of Filipino cuisine into this burger! Tender pork patties are tossed in a garlicky, sweet and savoury glaze, then stacked between toasted brioche buns with adobo-style caramelized onions, crispy fried eggs and chili-garlic mayo.
